Create Virtual environment using Virtualenv env_name
Activate the env using source env_name/Scripts/activate
Install django using pip install django
Create the project using django-admin startproject project_name
Test running the server: python manage.py runserver
Create the apps: python manage.py startapp app_name
Add the app_name to INSTALLED_APPS in Settings.py file
Migrate the database: python manage.py migrate
create super user: python manage.py createsuperuser
